mbledore hold the key to the Dark Lords weaknesses... until a shocking reversal exposes Dumbledores own vulnerabilities, and casts Harrysand Hogwartssfuture in shadow.',2015,4.56,652,1944099,27.69,'action_adventure'),(2688,9780440182931,'Suffer the Children',NULL,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=K0f_4ezr5nYC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','100 years after a young girls murder, children are again disappearing from Port Arbello.',1989,3.91,378,27480,50.18,'science_fiction'),(2689,9780440184621,'TaiPan','A Novel of Hong Kong','http://books.google.com/books/content?id=1NWMDQAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','Dick Straun, a pirate, smuggler, and ruthless individual, finds glory beyond his dreams as the TaiPan, or supreme leader, of Hong Kong. Reissue.',1966,4.27,734,38015,67.83,'action_adventure'),(2694,9780440208143,'An Acceptable Time',NULL,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=TIO416kel1oC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','A quiet visit with her grandparents turns into a lesson in the fluidity of time for Polly OKeefe when she meets several strangers from overlapping temporal planes and, with them, plays a key role in a prehistoric confrontation.',1990,3.82,343,15906,24.02,'fantasy'),(2696,9780440214922,'Drawing Blood',NULL,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=GsuXYyTNlMkC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','Twenty years after his tortured cartoonist father killed his mother and siblings, cartoonist Trevor McGee returns to the scene of the crime, determined to face the demons of the past and the dark force threatening to destroy him',1994,4.03,416,8674,76.65,'thriller'),(2697,9780440215813,'The Blue Knight',NULL,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=YrYe43nRm0wC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','Dont pass up the incredible values offered in this months 3.99 promotion with Robert B. Parkers Spenser novel, Pale Kings and Princes, John Sauls terrifying Comes the Bl