at family to pieces with her bare hands than see Maddy associate with a McKinnon. Its Romeo and Juliet all over again. Quick, hide those sharp knives and that little bottle of poison...',2004,3.79,448,4713,36.9,'action_adventure'),(4502,9780756400439,'In Conquest Born',NULL,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=UWnCk-wo5OAC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','Zatar and Anzha, the powerful opposing generals of the Braxana and Azeans, are determined to use the war between their peoples to settle a personal feud. Reprint.',2001,3.88,530,2426,48.82,'thriller'),(4503,9780756400613,'The Serpents Shadow',NULL,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=PAHin0_vSZ4C&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','From the magical mysteries of India to the gaslit streets of Victorian London, Mercedes Lackeys unique departure from her Valdemar series follows a young woman doctor as she searches for the secret behind the sorcery in her blood.',2002,3.99,394,8533,72.23,'fantasy'),(4504,9780756401108,'Sorcery Rising',NULL,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=VFgWzQEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','A talented knifemaker with a natural affinity with the elements of the earth, Katla Aransen, the beautiful and rebellious daughter of an Eyran merchant, finds herself targeted by Istrian fanatics after she accidentally commits sacrilege and by Saro Katla, a bladeforger and Saro, the second son of an Istrian noblemanare forever changed.',2003,3.55,528,1290,24.69,'science_fiction'),(4505,9780756401535,'Joust',NULL,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=RcWnDAEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','Vetch, an Altan serf, must learn the secret of the Tian jousters and their dragons in order to save his people.',2004,4.01,448,9871,76.73,'action_adventure'),(4506,9780756401818,'The War of the Flowers',NULL,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=Yofu6U2ocO8C&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','When his music car